Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:52.66,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ồ, thế thì thật trùng hợp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.21,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bay lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:09.48,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ê!
